; steps to reproduce the bug:
; 1. Run this code.
; 2. Click Drawing -> Download -> to SVG
; 3. Look at the SVG export.  Notice that a big rounded rect shows when it shouldn't.
make "radius 100
make "arcAngle 70
make "innerPeddleArcs [
	[:arcAngle / 2 0] [-:arcAngle 0.58] [(:arcAngle - 180) / 2 0] 
]
setPenSize 0
setFillColor "blue
polyStart
arcLines :innerPeddleArcs :radius
arcLines reverse :innerPeddleArcs :radius
polyEnd